  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat (400°F).",
    "Thread pork, chicken, red bell pepper, onion, and garlic onto skewers, leaving space between each piece.",
    "Brush olive oil on both sides of the meat and vegetables.",
    "Season with oregano, salt, pepper, and paprika.",
    "Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes on each side, or until cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, mix Worcestershire sauce with chimichurri in a small bowl.",
    "Brush the sauce mixture onto the skewers during the last 2 minutes of cooking.",
    "Remove skewers from grill and let rest for 2 minutes before serving."
